{title: I Can’t Take Another Heartache}
{artist: John Anderson}
{composer: Written by Roger Murrah and Scott Anders}

[C]Lips tell me she was lying
[F]Eyes tell me you’re not crying
[G7]Arms tell me you’re not empty [C]now
Hands say that you’re not shaking
[F]Mind hear that silence breaking
[G7]Please help me stop the pain some[C]how
I can’t [F]take another [C]heartache
And I’m [G7]so afraid it’s [C]too late
I can [F]feel the hurt it’s [C]starting
I can’t [G7]take another [C]heartache
Time must you keep me waiting
